item.title: CVE-2019-9703|2024-08-04T21:54:45.155Z -- symantec -- endpoint%20encryption
item.description: Symantec Endpoint Encryption, prior to SEE 11.3.0, may be susceptible to a privilege escalation vulnerability, which is a type of issue that allows a user to gain elevated access to resources that are normally protected at lower access levels.
